==Spanish==

===Etymology===
Unknown

===Transitive verb===
'''tirar'''

# to [[throw]]
# to [[throw]] [[out]]
# to [[shoot]]; to [[launch]]
# to [[take]] (a [[photograph]])
# to [[print]]
# to [[knock]] [[over]]; to [[knock]] [[down]]
# (''Spain'') (''vulg'') To [[fuck]]

====Synonyms====
*[[botar]] (2)
*[[echar]] (1)
*[[fotografiar]] (4)
*[[imprimir]] (5)

===Intransitive verb===
'''tirar'''

# to [[pull]]
# to [[shoot]]
# to [[manage]]; to [[get]] [[by]]
#: '''''tiramos''', es difícil, pero '''tiramos''''' - "we get by, it is hard, but we get by"
# to [[attract]]
'''tirar a'''
# to [[be]] [[somewhat]]
#: ''tira a lastima'' - "it is a bit sad"

===Reflexive Verb===
'''tirarse'''

# to [[throw]] [[oneself]]
# (''colloquial'') to [[spend]] [[time]]

